BTTTriggers.BTTShellTaskActionScript:
echo -e "GET http://google.com HTTP/1.0\n\n" | nc google.com 80 > /dev/null 2>&1

if [ $? -eq 0 ]; then
    echo 'Up'
else
    echo 'Down'
fi

BTTTriggers.BTTPredefinedActionName: Run Apple Script in background (enter directly as text)
BTTTriggers.BTTInlineAppleScript: tell application "iTunes"	if player state is paused then		return play	else		return pause	end ifend tell
